OL,3,CMan jailed for risking lives of
OL,4,Cfamilies in high-rise in Nottingham
OL,5,Cafter fire
OL,7,FA man who risked the lives of families
OL,8,Fin a high-rise tower block in
OL,9,FNottingham after setting fire to it
OL,10,Fhas been jailed.
OL,12,F45-year-old Richard Blunt had started
OL,13,Fthe blaze in Southchurch Court in
OL,14,FClifton on March 30th.
OL,16,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,17,F16th floor of the 20-storey building,
OL,18,Ffollowing reports a smoke alarm had
OL,19,Fbeen activated.
