OL,7,FNottinghamshire Fire and Rescue
OL,8,FService crews arrived on scene within
OL,9,Fminutes and quickly formulated a plan,
OL,10,Fwith smoke billowing from the front
OL,11,Fdoor of the two-bedroom flat.
OL,13,FAlmost every room was thick with toxic
OL,14,Fsmoke, with zero visibility, as crew
OL,15,Fmembers entered.
OL,17,FThey used a thermal imaging camera to
OL,18,Flocate the scene of the fire and used
OL,19,Fhose reel jets to put it out before
OL,20,Fsearching the rest of the property and
OL,21,Fchecking the welfare of residents.
