OL,7,FA positive pressure fan was used to
OL,8,Fclear the smoke.
OL,10,FAn investigation found he'd attempted
OL,11,Fto set a sofa alight with a can of
OL,12,Flighter fluid.
OL,14,FAs well as a pile of clothes and boxes
OL,15,Fin the hallway. Roads had to be closed
OL,16,Faround the area but no evacuation was
OL,17,Fneeded after crew members established
OL,18,Fthe fire was isolated to the flat.
