OL,3,CMan jailed for risking lives of
OL,4,Cfamilies in high-rise in Nottingham
OL,5,Cafter fire
OL,7,FFollowing inquiries into the fire,
OL,8,Fpolice stopped and arrested Blunt
OL,9,Fnearby around 40 minutes later.
OL,11,FBlunt, who was also in possession of a
OL,12,Fquantity of cannabis, was questioned
OL,13,Fand subsequently charged.
OL,15,FHe pleaded guilty to arson with
OL,16,Frecklessness as to whether life was
OL,17,Fendangered and possession of cannabis.
OL,19,FHe was sentenced to three years in
OL,20,Fprison when he appeared at Nottingham
OL,21,FCrown Court on Friday (4 October).
