OL,3,CMan jailed for risking lives of
OL,4,Cfamilies in high-rise in Nottingham
OL,5,Cafter fire
OL,7,FHe had previously been fined #80 for
OL,8,Fpossession of cannabis when he
OL,9,Fappeared at Nottingham Magistrates'
OL,10,FCourt on 1 April.
OL,12,FIn mitigation, the court heard that
OL,13,FBlunt had mental health difficulties
OL,14,Fat the time of the offence, aggravated
OL,15,Fby alcohol use.
OL,17,FIt was also accepted that Blunt had
OL,18,Fshown remorse and taken steps to
OL,19,Faddress his alcohol addiction.
